<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.7">
<l>kaṇṇaṉ maṉattuḷḷē niṟkavuṅ kaivaḷaikaḷ</l>
<l>eṉṉō kaḻaṉṟa vivaiyeṉṉa māyaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>peṇṇāṉōm peṇmaiyōm niṟka vavaṉmēya</l>
<l>vaṇṇal malaiyu maraṅkamum pāṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although Kaṇṇaṉ stays in my inner mind, why do my bangles slip off?</l>
<l>What are these wonders? We are women,</l>
<l>We of modesty; let [that] be. Of the lofty mountain where he dwells</l>
<l>And of Araṅkam, do we not sing?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
